{"tid":1605821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】哈利波特都走出嚟支持香港示威","createTime":"2019-09-30T11:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T11:58:55.000Z","uid":319080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"28407c457807feedae9cd1e672d4ad7f95d9b8e1","tid":1605821,"uid":319080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wZpEhKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwZpEhKM.jpg&h=46f3c631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ukDyh7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ukDyh7.jpg&h=9902ab6c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n警斥「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">世上沒火魔法師</span></span>」 哈利波特裝扮示威者向政總擲物<br />\n有網民今日（29日）發起遊行，計劃由銅鑼灣崇光百貨外的軒尼詩道，遊行至金鐘政府總部，惟遊行未獲警方不反對通知，警方曾舉藍旗，警告在場人士正在參與未經批准的集結，或會遭檢控。期間，防暴警察與示威者多次爆發激烈衝突，有激進示威者投擲汽油彈。<br />\n警察公共關係科高級警司（媒體聯絡及傳訊）江永祥早前曾稱：「我哋依家唔係玩角色扮演遊戲，呢個世界裡面係冇火魔法師架，我哋見到就只有縱火狂徒。」今日（29日）有示威者身穿酷似著名電影作品《哈利波特》中「霍格華茲魔法學校」的巫師服，手持掃把現身示威現場，並曾向政府總部投擲物品。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/380630/9-29-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%A5-%E4%B8%96%E4%B8%8A%E6%B2%92%E7%81%AB%E9%AD%94%E6%B3%95%E5%B8%AB-%E5%93%88%E5%88%A9%E6%B3%A2%E7%89%B9%E8%A3%9D%E6%89%AE%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%90%91%E6%94%BF%E7%B8%BD%E6%93%B2%E7%89%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F380630%2F9-29-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25A5-%25E4%25B8%2596%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B2%2592%25E7%2581%25AB%25E9%25AD%2594%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25B8%25AB-%25E5%2593%2588%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E7%2589%25B9%25E8%25A3%259D%25E6%2589%25AE%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E6%2593%25B2%25E7%2589%25A9&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=6b158ac6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/380630/9-29-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%A5-%E4%B8%96%E4%B8%8A%E6%B2%92%E7%81%AB%E9%AD%94%E6%B3%95%E5%B8%AB-%E5%93%88%E5%88%A9%E6%B3%A2%E7%89%B9%E8%A3%9D%E6%89%AE%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%90%91%E6%94%BF%E7%B8%BD%E6%93%B2%E7%89%A9</a>"},{"pid":"39241a3f72a0f09b6e1bfa7c4480830abcc3142a","tid":1605821,"uid":313054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64690a460e967fa62abc72979342cce8ff78958","tid":1605821,"uid":319080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hJPMHeQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJPMHeQ.gif&h=27882d01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0401e6700d778d5164623200416e71011783a9d","tid":1605821,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"葛萊芬多加五分"}]}